tcp: add ca_state stat in SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS

This patch adds TCP_NLA_CA_STATE stat into SCM_TIMESTAMPING_OPT_STATS.
It reports ca_state of socket, when timestamp is generated.

